OL,3,CFarage tops list of MPs' outside
OL,4,Cearnings, making #43,000 for filming
OL,5,CCameos
OL,7,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage topped
OL,8,Fthe list of MPs' outside earnings,
OL,9,Freporting #43,548.76 of income from
OL,10,Frecording 30 hours of personalised
OL,11,FCameo videos.
OL,13,FThe Clacton MP logged these earnings
OL,14,Fover the past four months, adding to
OL,15,Fthe #81,634 the videos had already
OL,16,Fearned him over the last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
