CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774465894
OL,3,CFarage tops list of MPs' outside
OL,4,Cearnings, making #43,000 for filming
OL,5,CCameos
OL,7,FMPs are required by law to declare all
OL,8,Fincome they make from outside sources
OL,9,Fwithin 28 days of receiving the money.
OL,10,FThey are also required to register all
OL,11,Fgifts and donations they receive over
OL,12,Fthe value of #300.
OL,14,FITV News has reached out to Reform UK
OL,15,Ffor further comment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
