OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774465894
OL,3,CFarage tops list of MPs' outside
OL,4,Cearnings, making #43,000 for filming
OL,5,CCameos
OL,7,FFarage has previously apologised for
OL,8,Ffailing to report outside earnings
OL,9,Fwithin the required timeframe after
OL,10,Fthe parliamentary standards watchdog
OL,11,Ffound he had breached the MPs' code of
OL,12,Fconduct 17 times by failing to
OL,13,Fregister #384,000 in earnings.
OL,15,FCameo is a video platform used by
OL,16,Fcelebrities and public figures that
OL,17,Fallows the public to purchase
OL,18,Fpersonalised video messages.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
