CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774465894
OL,3,CFarage tops list of MPs' outside
OL,4,Cearnings, making #43,000 for filming
OL,5,CCameos
OL,7,FFarage's use of the platform made
OL,8,Fheadlines last week when an
OL,9,Finvestigation by the Guardian revealed
OL,10,Fhe had recorded multiple messages
OL,11,Fendorsing a neo-Nazi event, repeating
OL,12,Fextremist slogans, and making
OL,13,Fmisogynistic remarks.
OL,15,FThe Guardian also reported that Farage
OL,16,Fcharged #155 for a video to a man he
OL,17,Fwas told had received a 16-month
OL,18,Fsentence for his involvement in a far-
OL,19,Fright riot. The Reform leader told the
OL,20,Fman to "keep acting in the right way",
OL,21,Fthe video shows.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774465894
OL,3,CFarage tops list of MPs' outside
OL,4,Cearnings, making #43,000 for filming
OL,5,CCameos
OL,7,FFarage declined to comment on the
OL,8,Finvestigation last week, saying "I
OL,9,Fdon't approve of things being
OL,10,Fpublished in national newspapers on
OL,11,Fthings that have been illegally
OL,12,Fobtained".
OL,14,FResponding, a Guardian spokesperson
OL,15,Ftold ITV News: "Nigel Farage's
OL,16,Fallegation is entirely false. All of
OL,17,Fthe Cameo videos and their associated
OL,18,Fdata used in our investigation were
OL,19,Fpublicly available on the platform's
OL,20,Fwebsite."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
