OL,3,CFarage tops list of MPs' outside
OL,4,Cearnings, making #43,000 for filming
OL,5,CCameos
OL,7,FFarage declined to comment on his
OL,8,Finappropriate Cameo videos when asked
OL,9,Fby ITV News last week
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the Reform UK
OL,12,Fleader said: "Mr Farage has recorded
OL,13,Fmany thousands of videos for genuine
OL,14,Fsupporters to celebrate weddings,
OL,15,Fcongratulate friends or send novelty
OL,16,Fmessages. At that scale, the
OL,17,Foccasional mistake can occur.
OL,19,F"(They) should not be treated as
OL,20,Fpolitical statements or campaign
OL,21,Factivity.
