OL,3,CFarage tops list of MPs' outside
OL,4,Cearnings, making #43,000 for filming
OL,5,CCameos
OL,7,F"He has long been clear in his
OL,8,Fopposition to extremism and political
OL,9,Fviolence."
OL,11,FThe Reform leader has previously
OL,12,Fcaused controversy with his Cameo
OL,13,Fvideos after repeating a pro-IRA
OL,14,Fslogan in one message requested by a
OL,15,Fcustomer.
OL,17,FAs of March 25, Farage has stopped
OL,18,Ftaking Cameo requests, with users
OL,19,Fbeing told "Nigel Farage is
OL,20,Funavailable" when viewing his profile.
OL,26,@qD@JO]
