OL,3,CFarage tops list of MPs' outside
OL,4,Cearnings, making #43,000 for filming
OL,5,CCameos
OL,7,FA Reform Party spokesperson said
OL,8,FFarage had paused his account "for
OL,9,Fsecurity reasons".
OL,11,FAshton under Lyne MP Angela Rayner
OL,12,Frecorded the second-highest earnings,
OL,13,Fregistering a payment of #19,000 for a
OL,14,Fspeaking engagement via JLA Speakers
OL,15,FLtd on February 13.
OL,17,FWhat are the rules around outside
OL,18,Fearnings and gifts for MPs?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774465894
OL,3,CFarage tops list of MPs' outside
OL,4,Cearnings, making #43,000 for filming
OL,5,CCameos
OL,7,FNo cap exists on the amount MPs can
OL,8,Fearn from outside employment, though
OL,9,Fsome groups have called for limits on
OL,10,Fwhat is allowed.
OL,12,FMPs are currently forbidden from
OL,13,Fworking as paid strategists, advisers,
OL,14,For consultants, or from lobbying
OL,15,Fministers on behalf of outside
OL,16,Finterests.
OL,18,FRules also stipulate they must not be
OL,19,Fprevented from fulfilling their
OL,20,Fprimary duties to constituents by
OL,21,Fexternal work.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774465894
OL,3,CFarage tops list of MPs' outside
OL,4,Cearnings, making #43,000 for filming
OL,5,CCameos
OL,7,FThe rules for gifts, however, are much
OL,8,Ftighter.
OL,10,FMPs can only receive gifts or
OL,11,Fdonations worth over #500 from
OL,12,Findividuals on the UK electoral
OL,13,Fregister, UK-registered companies and
OL,14,Fsome UK-registered organisations.
OL,16,FThey cannot accept gifts worth over
OL,17,F#500 from foreign individuals or
OL,18,Fcompanies registered outside the UK,
OL,19,Fexcept in the case of overseas travel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
