OL,3,CFarage tops list of MPs' outside
OL,4,Cearnings, making #43,000 for filming
OL,5,CCameos
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe rules for ministers are even
OL,13,Fstricter, after Starmer sought greater
OL,14,Ftransparency over what was allowed.
OL,16,FA separate register of interests for
OL,17,Fgifts received in ministerial
OL,18,Fcapacities exists and is published by
OL,19,Fthe Cabinet Office each month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
