PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774465894
OL,3,CFarage tops list of MPs' outside
OL,4,Cearnings, making #43,000 for filming
OL,5,CCameos
OL,7,FMinisters can keep gifts worth up to
OL,8,F#140 and do not have to declare them `
OL,9,Fif the gift is of higher value, they
OL,10,Fcan choose to pay the difference
OL,11,Fbetween the value and #140 to purchase
OL,12,Fit, as Starmer chose to do for a pair
OL,13,Fof personalised cufflinks Donald Trump
OL,14,Fgifted his son during the president's
OL,15,Fsecond state visit.
OL,17,FAnything not purchased by a minister
OL,18,Fmust be given back to the department
OL,19,Fin which they work.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
