OL,7,FOn Wednesday, the government announced
OL,8,Fnew measures to tighten the
OL,9,Frestrictions on donations from dual
OL,10,FBritish nationals as well as foreign
OL,11,Findividuals hoping to donate money
OL,12,Fthrough UK companies.
